OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEx-NBA star's Taiwan       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcomment sparks China anger 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Basketball star Dwight Howard has drawn
OL,6, a fierce backlash in China after he    
OL,7, called Taiwan a "country" in a video.  
OL,9,FThe 37-year-old American's comments    
OL,10,Fcame in a commercial appearance        
OL,11,Falongside Taiwan's vice-president.     
OL,13,FHis remark was criticised as advocating
OL,14,F"Taiwan independence" in China, which  
OL,15,Fsees the island as a breakaway         
OL,16,Fprovince.                              
OL,18,FHoward later told local media: "If I   
OL,19,Foffended anyone in China, anybody you  
OL,20,Fknow, I apologise."                    
